{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require the installation and use of safety belts in police vans",
        "additional_details": "We think the law should be changed: Require safety seatbelts in the back of police vans for the safety of people being transport, especially in case there is an accident on the way to custody. ",
        "background": "There is currently not a legal duty on police services to have seatbelts installed and used for detainees who are being transported in vans. ",
